and participate in all strategic and policy decisions affecting its operations he served as the head of corporate  legal  compliance and executive vice president at siemens aktiengesellschaft also known as siemens ag until december   and its general counsel and member of management board from october   to december   with responsibility for siemens businesses in the americas he served as the acting chief compliance officer of siemens aktiengesellschaft from may  to june  he served as a member of the managing board at the siemens automation and drives group siemens metering communications and services he served as general counsel of ge healthcare limited since november  and also served as its executive vicepresident he served as vice president and general counsel at ge medical systems a general electric company since  he was attorney specializing in securities law at ballard spahr andrews  ingersoll and philadelphia pennsylvania usa since  he served as law clerk at united states federal district court judge clarence c newcomer in the federal district court for the eastern district of pennsylvania since  before joining ge healthcare mr solmssen served as vice president and general counsel at ge advanced materials formerly ge plastics from  to november  he served as vice president and general counsel of general electric company  ge medical systems waukesha wi usa since  before joining ge he served as a senior partner in the law firm of morgan lewis  bockius since  he was a leader in morgan lewis  bockiuss international and corporate practice he served as the chairman of siemens corporation until december   and is its director he serves as vice chairman of the german american chamber of commerce in new york and the chairman of the  united way of waukesha campaign he served as a director of nokia networks and nokia solutions and networks oy he was articles editor of the law review of university of pennsylvania mr solmssen received his ab in history and literature from harvard university was a knox fellow scholarship program at oxford university and received his law degree from the university of pennsylvaniaread full background corporate headquarters  water streetnew york new york united statesphone fax  board members memberships directorsiemens corporation education ba harvard universityllb university of pennsylvania other affiliations siemens corporationharvard universitysiemens aktiengesellschaftge healthcare limiteduniversity of pennsylvaniasiemens metering communications and servicesnokia solutions and networks oynokia networks annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data available total compensation there is no total compensation data available request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup competitor compensationnamepositioncompanycompensationdavid m cordani chief executive officer president and directorcigna corporationmsteven a kandarian jdchairman president  ceometlife incmevan g greenberg chairman ceo chairman of chubb group and ceo of chubb groupchubb limitedmmark t bertolini chairman and chief executive officeraetna incmjohn robert strangfeld jrchairman and chief executive officerprudential financial incmcompensation as of fiscal year  sponsored financial commentaries sponsored links browse companies a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z              request profile update only a company representative may request an update for the company profile documentation will be required to contact american international group inc please visit  company data is provided by sp global market intelligence please use this form to report any data