 ge in  as vice president and general counsel of ge plastics in pittsfield massachusetts from  to  solmssen was a senior partner in the law firm of morgan lewis  bockius llp of philadelphia he was in charge of the firms frankfurt am main office specializing in ma and securities law one of his notable transactions was the listing of sap ag on the new york stock exchange solmssen started his career as an attorney at the law firm of ballard spahr andrews  ingersoll in philadelphia from  to  before that he served as a law clerk for us federal district court judge clarence c newcomer from  to  solmssen received his jd cum laude from the university of pennsylvania in philadelphia where he was articles editor of the university of pennsylvania law review and his ab magna cum laude from harvard university he also studied law at brasenose college oxford university uk on a knox fellowship solmssen was born on january   in philadelphia he speaks fluent german tweets by acilegal latest blog posts hear from top fda regulatory experts at aci’s th annual fda boot camp devices edition pharmaceuticals  biotech  life sciences by american conference institute  jun   aci’s fda boot camp to feature a “who’s who” of the fda regulatory bar pharmaceuticals  biotech  life sciences by american conference institute  jun   highlights of keynote address at aci’s brazil summit on anticorruption anticorruption  fcpa by american conference institute  may   law highlights aci pto proceedings ptab judges roundtable intellectual property by american conference institute  may   aci’s pto proceedings covered by law intellectual property by american conference institute  may   view conferences by location by sector featured view cart continue shopping close peter solmssen  abebooks abebookscom passion for books sign onmy accountbasket help search by keyword by title by author by isbn by publisher by collection find advanced search item added to your basket view basket order total  item items shipping des